Your spells and abilities have a chance to activate Healing Tide Totem for 35% of its base duration.

When the Vision of Perfection activates, you and up to 2 other nearby allies gain 4 Haste for 10 sec.

passive_spell_tooltip.description:
Reduces the cooldown of Healing Tide Totem by 10.0%, and increases your Versatility by 3.

When you activate Healing Tide Totem, immediately heal for 5% of maximum health.
Your heals have a chance to grant either 25 Intellect for 10 sec or 104 mana. Chance of receiving mana increases with your missing mana. 20% chance to gain both effects.

Each time any ally within 40 yds uses an Azerite Essence, gain 5 Intellect and 3 Haste for 20 sec.

The ally who used an Azerite Essence also gains 3 Haste for 20 sec. Only one ally can have this Haste effect at a time.

Unique: Corruption Resistance increased by 10.
Every 1-25 sec, a Lifeblood Shard erupts from the nearby ground for 18 sec.
